<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">والنَّصِيْصُ:</span> غَلَيَانُ القِدْرِ، نَصَّتِ القِدْرُ نَصِيْصاً.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وكانَ نَصِيْصُ القَوْمِ كذا:</span> أي عَدَدُهم.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">والنَّصَّةُ:</span> العُصْفُوْرَةُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">والنُّصَّةُ:</span> الخُصْلَةُ من الشَّعر.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>